  <name>MultiCode AI Bot</name>
  <summary>Multi-AI Telegram Bot with 8 AI Providers</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      MultiCode AI Bot is a powerful Telegram bot that provides remote access to 8 different AI coding assistants,
      enabling developers to interact with their projects from anywhere with the perfect AI for each task.
    </p>
    <p>
      Supported AI Providers:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Claude - Premium quality, exceptional reasoning</li>
      <li>Gemini - FREE tier, 1M context window</li>
      <li>OpenAI GPT-4 - Industry standard</li>
      <li>DeepSeek - Ultra-cheap code specialist ($0.14/1M tokens)</li>
      <li>Groq - Ultra-fast LPU inference (FREE)</li>
      <li>Ollama - 100% local, privacy-focused (FREE)</li>
      <li>Blackbox - Code-focused web API (FREE)</li>
      <li>Windsurf - Codeium cascade (FREE)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

